{"type":"message","id":"82f28baf","parentId":"eb6a9821","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:41:49.122Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sessions are restricted to the current session tree. I can only send to sessions within my current WeChat session tree. I cannot directly send to the Feishu session from here.\n\nThis is a limitation of the current setup. The Feishu and WeChat sessions are separate session trees. I would need to either:\n\n1. Find the Feishu session key within the current tree\n2. Use the Feishu API/skill directly to send a message\n3. Ask the user to do it from the Feishu side\n\nLet me check if there's a way to route through the Feishu skill/tools directly. Actually, I could try to use the Feishu IM tools to send a message directly. But that would require knowing the user's Feishu open_id and using the Feishu API.\n\n\nThe sessions_list tool only showed me the WeChat session, so the Feishu session might be in a different session tree entirely. The error about visibility being restricted to the current tree suggests I can't access it from here, which means I likely can't initiate a message to WeChat from within the Feishu session tree either.\n\nI should just explain this limitation to the user directly and suggest they test it from the Feishu side themselves."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 抱歉，有几个问题：\n\n1. **跨 Session Tree 限制**：飞书（Kate）和微信是两个独立的会话树，我不能从微信这边直接调用飞书 session 给你发消息\n2. **之前没回复的原因**：16:30、16:57、17:04 那几条消息我没有收到——可能是 WebSocket 连接断过，或者那段时候正好有 session 隔离\n\n**测试建议**：你可以直接在飞书那边对 Kate 说\"给我发微信测试\"，或者反过来在微信这边测试飞书。\n\n需要我帮你排查一下消息接收的问题吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775659296518,"responseId":"06259c2082fc66d4dc8887f87c52f551"}}
